# plengo-data-infra-v2

ETL pipeline platform and analytics dashboards for Plengo data monitoring and decision-making.  
Built on **Apache Airflow 2.6**, **PostgreSQL**, **Redis (Celery)**, and a lightweight **Flask Web UI**.

---

